From: opencode-ai formula (OHOS)
Subject: web command — 无 DISPLAY 时不调 open()

现象: opencode web 在无头 linux/openharmony 环境也会调 open() →
spawn xdg-open ENOENT。原 guard 只排 linux，编译产物
process.platform === "openharmony" 时恒为真，同样会触发。

为什么这么改: DISPLAY/WAYLAND_DISPLAY 缺失时跳过 open()；platform
检查同时排除 linux 与 openharmony。

何时可删除: 上游化 PR（无头 linux 同样不该调 open()），合并后即删。

diff --git a/packages/opencode/src/cli/cmd/web.ts b/packages/opencode/src/cli/cmd/web.ts
index 69a981aad..6b586d51f 100644
--- a/packages/opencode/src/cli/cmd/web.ts
+++ b/packages/opencode/src/cli/cmd/web.ts
@@ -72,11 +72,15 @@ export const WebCommand = effectCmd({
       }
 
       // Open localhost in browser
-      open(localhostUrl).catch(() => {})
+      if (process.env.DISPLAY || process.env.WAYLAND_DISPLAY || (process.platform !== "linux" && process.platform !== "openharmony")) {
+        open(localhostUrl).catch(() => {})
+      }
     } else {
       const displayUrl = server.url.toString()
       UI.println(UI.Style.TEXT_INFO_BOLD + "  Web interface:    ", UI.Style.TEXT_NORMAL, displayUrl)
-      open(displayUrl).catch(() => {})
+      if (process.env.DISPLAY || process.env.WAYLAND_DISPLAY || (process.platform !== "linux" && process.platform !== "openharmony")) {
+        open(displayUrl).catch(() => {})
+      }
     }
 
     yield* Effect.never
